          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "settings": {
            "html": "<!-- PROCESS -->\n<section class=\"mint\" id=\"process\">\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"sect-head\">\n      <span class=\"eyebrow\">The Midland Process Explained</span>\n      <h2>How our process works.</h2>\n      <p class=\"lede\">\n        Our process makes it easy to see exactly how we deliver quality results and complete client satisfaction. Clear steps, no guesswork, and a smooth experience from first visit to final clean.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"process-row reveal\">\n      <div class=\"process-step\">\n        <div class=\"circle-wrap\"><div class=\"circle\">SITE</div><div class=\"badge\">01</div></div>\n        <h4>Walkthrough</h4>\n        <p>We inspect the space in person, identify surfaces and trouble spots.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"process-step\">\n        <div class=\"circle-wrap\"><div class=\"circle\">PLAN</div><div class=\"badge\">02</div></div>\n        <h4>Facility Score</h4>\n        <p>You get a written assessment of every surface. Yours to keep.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"process-step\">\n        <div class=\"circle-wrap\"><div class=\"circle\">QUOTE</div><div class=\"badge\">03</div></div>\n        <h4>24-48 Hour Quote</h4>\n        <p>Line-item pricing, no hidden fees, no annual lock-ins.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"process-step\">\n        <div class=\"circle-wrap\"><div class=\"circle\">CLEAN</div><div class=\"badge\">04</div></div>\n        <h4>Schedule</h4>\n        <p>Nights, weekends, holidays. Your tenants only see the result.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
          },
          "elements": [],
          "isInner": false
        }
      ],
      "isInner": false
