          "id": "3fabaeef",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "settings": {
            "html": "<!-- FAQ (lightweight) -->\n<section id=\"faq\" class=\"mint\">\n  <div class=\"wrap-narrow\">\n    <div class=\"sect-head\">\n      <span class=\"eyebrow\">FAQ</span>\n      <h2>Questions DMV homeowners and facility managers ask first.</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;gap:10px\">\n      <details style=\"background:#FFF; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px;\">\n        <summary style=\"list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:18px; font-size:16px; font-weight:800; cursor:pointer\">How fast can you get on-site? <span style=\"width:24px;height:24px;background:var(--mint);color:var(--green-deep);border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800\">+</span></summary>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:12px;color:var(--ink-2);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6\">Most DMV clients get a site visit within 48 hours and a written quote 24-48 hours after. Same-day emergency dispatch. Call (240) 532-9097.</div>\n      </details>\n      <details style=\"background:#FFF; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px;\">\n        <summary style=\"list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:18px; font-size:16px; font-weight:800; cursor:pointer\">Are you insured and COI-ready? <span style=\"width:24px;height:24px;background:var(--mint);color:var(--green-deep);border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800\">+</span></summary>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:12px;color:var(--ink-2);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6\">Yes. Fully insured. COI, W-9, and SDS sheets are emailed the same business day you ask.</div>\n      </details>\n      <details style=\"background:#FFF; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px;\">\n        <summary style=\"list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:18px; font-size:16px; font-weight:800; cursor:pointer\">Do you handle nights, weekends, and emergencies? <span style=\"width:24px;height:24px;background:var(--mint);color:var(--green-deep);border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800\">+</span></summary>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:12px;color:var(--ink-2);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6\">Yes. Most commercial work happens nights, weekends, and holidays. Same-day emergency response is available. Call (240) 532-9097.</div>\n      </details>\n      <details style=\"background:#FFF; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px;\">\n        <summary style=\"list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:18px; font-size:16px; font-weight:800; cursor:pointer\">What's the difference vs. national chains? <span style=\"width:24px;height:24px;background:var(--mint);color:var(--green-deep);border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800\">+</span></summary>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:12px;color:var(--ink-2);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6\">We're a local DMV flooring contractor, not a national franchise. One named account lead, custom programs, faster response, no annual lock-ins.</div>\n      </details>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
          },
